Usage: vehicle check (-s|--specification FILE) [-t|--typeSystem TYPE_SYSTEM]

  Type-check a .vcl specification file.

Available options:
  -s,--specification FILE  The .vcl file containing the specification.
  -t,--typeSystem TYPE_SYSTEM
                           A secondary type system to be used. 1. Polarity -
                           check whether alternating quantifiers are used in the
                           specification. 2. Linearity - check whether
                           quantified variables are used linearly in the
                           specification. 3. Decidability - check which booleans
                           are decidable and which are undecidable in the
                           context of Vehicle
  -h,--help                Show this help text
